 it has enjoyed enormous popularity, peaking in the 1960s. Among other famous bearers is the actress  Deborah Kerr  (  1921–2007 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Letitia de Lostock was born about 1146, in Lostock, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Gralam Fitzrichard de Runchamp."},"et":{"about 1146–":"umbes 1146–Surnud","1143–1234":"1143–1234","1168–1234":"1168–1234","1146–Female":"1146–Surnud","1168":"1168","1146":"1146","1234":"1234","1143":"1143","about 1146":"umbes 1146","Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, England":"Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, England","Lostock,Lancashire,England.":"Lostock, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1146–":"noin 1146–Kuollut","1143–1234":"1143–1234","1168–1234":"1168–1234","1146–Female":"1146–Kuollut","1168":"1168","1146":"1146","1234":"1234","1143":"1143","about 1146":"noin 1146","Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, England":"Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, England","Lostock,Lancashire,England.":"Lostock, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1146–":"environ 1146–Décédée","1143–1234":"1143–1234","1168–1234":"1168–1234","1146–Female":"1146–Décédée","1168":"1168","1146":"1146","1234":"1234","1143":"1143","about 1146":"environ 1146","Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, England":"Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, Angleterre","Lostock,Lancashire,England.":"Lostock, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Letitia de Lostock est née environ 1146, à Lostock, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Gralam Fitzrichard de Runchamp."},"de":{"about 1146–":"um 1146–Verstorben","1143–1234":"1143–1234","1168–1234":"1168–1234","1146–Female":"1146–Verstorben","1168":"1168","1146":"1146","1234":"1234","1143":"1143","about 1146":"um 1146","Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, England":"Lostock Gralam, Cheshire, England","Lostock,Lancashire,England.":"Lostock, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Letitia de Lostock wurde um 1146 in Lostock, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatt